OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy, with rain spreading in
OL,6,Ffrom the west, at times heavy. Winds
OL,7,Fgenerally light, though freshening
OL,8,Falong coasts during the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FRain becoming more isolated
OL,11,Fthrough the evening, mainly confined
OL,12,Fto the north of the region. A band of
OL,13,Fheavy, perhaps thundery, showers may
OL,14,Fmove north overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FAny early heavy, thundery,
OL,17,Fshowers soon clearing northeast to
OL,18,Fleave a dry but mostly cloudy day.
OL,19,FHazy sunshine developing into the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
