OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and sunny. Chance of thundery
OL,7,Fshowers developing later Thursday and
OL,8,Fcontinuing into early Friday. Widely
OL,9,Fvery warm, including at night.
